    <p>A young vis­i­tor wear­ing a face mask pass­ing through a colour­ful tun­nel at “Won­derLand”, a Christ­mas and win­ter-themed drive-through ex­pe­ri­ence in Wood­land Hills, Cal­i­for­nia, on Mon­day. The ex­pe­ri­ence, hon­our­ing all cul­tural tra­di­tions, started on Mon­day and will run un­til Dec 30. The ex­pe­ri­ence in­cludes spe­cial ap­pear­ances by Santa Claus, Mrs Claus and their elf helpers, and promised one-of-a-kind photo and video op­por­tu­ni­ties for hol­i­day cards that could be sent to fam­i­lies and friends.</p>

